N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 333.15 - Composition

State Regulations

There shall be a college administrative conference of
each college which shall be comprised of the chancellor, the chief
administrative officer of the college and such other persons as may be
designated by the chief administrative officer of the college. The chancellor, or if absent, the chief administrative officer of the college, shall be the
presiding officer of each college administrative conference. Notes
